It doesn&#39;t look like you&#39;re using the key being passed to your onClick handler. Try:
```javascript
checkboxClicked = (key) =&gt; {
  this.setState({ [key]: true })
}
```

and if you want it to be toggled:
```javascript
checkboxClicked = (key) =&gt; {
  this.setState({ [key]: !this.state[key] })
}

